      <title>富国生命预计日本央行加息将使日本国债收益率接近目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/fukoku-life-sees-boj-hikes-bringing-jgb-yields-toward-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国相互生命保险公司预计日本央行在3月底前将加息多达两次，并计划在适当的条件下投资日本超长期政府债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/fukoku-life-sees-boj-hikes-bringing-jgb-yields-toward-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
